AT|
Dee_Dee_20: I also considered 4nt but I thought Patti would take as quantitative.|
PG| ***** 13 ***** |


cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|4N is only quantitative if pard has bid NT. This is one area where I disagree with Marty Bergen, I think quantitative is not a good convention. too easy to get confused as to when it is or isn't.|
