AT| It shows a minimum of 16 or so with no upper limit and it is forcing to 2N at least. So, if responder wants to force to game, having at least a good 8, he or she has 2 choices. Responder can either keep the bidding below 2N, as Patti did, or bid 4sf. On most hands that works out okay. |
