NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|2N by responder is not a game force although most of the time it will get raised to 3N. So, if responder simply shows a preference for one of opener's suit, it is not forcing. That is how I play it. To force over a reverse, either bid 4sf or keep the bid below 2N or just bid game if you know where you want to play it. That is always an option.|
